        "value": 10
      },
      "disable": "<p>If the curse affecting Scarwall is lifted, this haunt fades away</p>",
      "description": "<p>Kitchen ovens haunted by those murdered inside them that shriek and burn anyone who comes near.</p><hr /><h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p>The ovens where Kazavon slow-roasted victims — and where Mandraivus's men threw the villainous cooks. Four humanoid outlines are burned into the brick; the ovens are still faintly warm.</p>",
      "reset": "<p>The haunt resets after 1 hour.</p>",
